doc_summary_long: The Girl Guides of Canada are cancelling all travel to the United States because of fears that their members might have trouble at the border due to travel restrictions enacted by Donald Trump. Kiriliuks said the Girl Guides didn't want to take the risk with all the uncertainty. 'This just speaks to the Girl Guides of Canada and our commitment to inclusivity,' Kiriliuks said.
doc_summary_short: The Girl Guides of Canada are cancelling all travel to the United States because of fears that their members might have trouble at the border due to travel restrictions enacted by Donald Trump.
doc_title: Canada's Girl Guides cancel all US travel as Trump rules spark fears at border.
